<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Can&apos;t believe the negative posts I&apos;m reading. Great gritty dark fantasy with three unique protagonists and very distinct voices for each. None of them<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Can't believe the negative posts I'm reading. Great gritty dark fantasy with three unique protagonists and very distinct voices for each. None of them are heroes per se, but all are interesting and compelling. Good read so far, fans of A Song of Ice and Fire may like it. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
