<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/177584-what-book-does-the-blade-itself-compare">What book does The Blade Itself compare to?
I have not read Joe Abercrombie&#39;s books but heard they were good..</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_177584'><a id="like_count_community_question_177584" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/177584?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F944073.The_Blade_Itself">like</a></span>

